Former Hai District Commissioner Lengai Ole Sabaya and his fellows have today (18 Friday, 2021) appeared before Arusha District Court to answer five charges facing them. Sabaya faces five charges including abuse of power, economic sabotage, money laundering, armed robbery and corruption. Before Sabaya arraigned at the court, May, this year, President Â Suluhu Hassan revoked appointment of the politician to pave a way for investigations.